, Provocative, Purposeful, Reassuring, Relaxing, Sensual, Sexy, Shocking, Soothing, Suspicious, Tender, Tentative, Thrilling, Tortuous, Uncomfortable, Unpleasant, Unsettling, Uplifting, Vague, Vivid, Warm<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Q373","QuestionID":"QID746","QuestionType":"TE","Selector":"ESTB","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"\u00a0 \u00a0 Need some inspiration? The touch is Aggressive, Alarming, Annoying, Arousing, Attention Grabb...","Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None","MinChars":"1"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"SearchSource":{"AllowFreeResponse":"false"},"DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_82HJZMMWolInCCi","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID733","SecondaryAttribute":"\u00a0 Here is the same video again, in case you want to re-watch it. For the following questions, ple..","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<h3 style=\"text-align: right;\">&nbsp;<\/h3>\n\n<h3><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Here is the same video again, in case you want to re-watch it. For the following questions, <strong>please keep in mind the social scenario you imagined on the previous page<\/strong>. <br><\/span><\/h3>\n\n<div>&nbsp;<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"padding:56.25% 0 0 0;position:relative;\"><iframe style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;\" src=\"${lm:\/\/Field\/1}\"><\/iframe><\/div>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Video_page2","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"\u00a0 Here is the same video again, in case you want to re-watch it. For the following questions, ple...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID733"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_82HJZMMWolInCCi","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID340","SecondaryAttribute":"\u00a0 How would you describe the physical characteristics of the touch in the video you just watched?..","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n<div><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">How would you describe the physical characteristics of the touch in the video you just watched?<\/span><\/div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;<\/div>\n\n<div><span style=\"font-size:13px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Need some inspiration?<\/span><\/span><\/div>\n\n<div id=\"accordion4\">\n<div>\n<h3><span style=\"font-size:13px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Verbs<\/span><\/span><\/h3>\n\n<div><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:107%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Burning, Buzzing, Catching, Compressing, Crawling, Dragging, Embracing, Fluttering,  Freezing, Friction, Grabbing, Hitting, Holding, Hugging, Interlocking, Lifting, Melting, Patting, Pinching, Poking, Pounding, Pressing, Punching, Pushing, Rubbing, Scratching, Shaking, Slapping, Squeezing, Stabbing, Stinging, Strangling, Stretching, Stroking, Sweeping, Swinging, Tapping, Trembling, Tickling, Vibrating<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div>\n<h3><span style=\"font-size:13px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Adjectives<\/span><\/span><\/h3>\n\n<div>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:107%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Abrasive, Bumpy, Chilly, Coarse, Cold, Consistent, Damp, Deadened, Dense, Diffuse, Dry, Fast, Feathery, Firm, Flat, Fleshy, Flexible, Fluid, Gelatinous, Granular, Greasy, Hairy, Hard, Hot, Intense, Irregular, Itchy, Leathery, Light, Localized, Lumpy, Lukewarm, Mechanical, Moist, Mushy, Oily, Persistent, Pointy, Powdery, Prickly, Ribbed, Rigid, Robust, Rough, Rubbery, Rhythmic, Scratchy, Sharp, Slippery, Slow, Smooth, Soft, Solid, Sticky, Strong, Supple, Sweaty, Tense, Textured, Tough, Transient, Uneven, Velvety, Warm, Weak, Wet, Wiggly, Wrinkly<\/span><\/span><\/span><br>\n&nbsp;<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>","QuestionJS":"Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnload(function()\n{\n\t\/*Place your JavaScript here to run when the page loads*\/\n\n});\n\nQualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnReady(function()\n{\n\t\/*Place your JavaScript here to run when the page is fully displayed*\/\n\t\tjQuery( function() {\n        jQuery( \"#accordion4 > div\" ).accordion({\n\t\t\theader: \"h3\",\n            active:false,\n            collapsible: true\n        });\n  } );\n\n});\n\nQualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnUnload(function()\n{\n\t\/*Place your JavaScript here to run when the page is unloaded*\/\n\n});","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Sensory_02","QuestionID":"QID340","QuestionType":"TE","Selector":"ESTB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"\u00a0 How would you describe the physical characteristics of the touch in the video you just watched?...","Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None","MinChars":"1"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"DE":{"QuestionText":"<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color:black\">Wie w\u00fcrden Sie die physischen Merkmale der Ber\u00fchrung, die sie sich gerade angesehen haben beschreiben?\u00a0<\/span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Brauchen Sie ein wenig<\/span><\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">\u00a0<button id=\"myBtn\">inspiration?<\/button> <\/span><\/p>\n\n<div class=\"modal\" id=\"myModal\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\"><span class=\"close\">\u00d7<\/span>\n\n<h3><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Physical characteristics<\/span><\/h3>\n<\/div>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Verben:<br \/>\ndr\u00fccken, Halten, klatschen, quetschen, reiben, schieben, sch\u00fctteln, schwingen, streicheln, stupsen, t\u00e4tscheln, tippen<br \/>\nAdjektive:<br \/>\nbrennend, derb, durchn\u00e4sst, eisig, fedrig, fest, fettig, feucht, flauschig, frigide, gefrierend, gerillt, gezackt, glatt, glitschig, grie\u00dfig, gummiartig, haarig, hart, hei\u00df, kalt, klamm, klebrig, klumpig, k\u00f6rnig, kratzig, k\u00fchl, langsam, ledrig, matschig, nass, \u00f6lig, pelzig, rau, samtig, sandig, scharf, schleimig, schmierig, schnell, schuppig, schwabbelig, schwach, schwammig, schwitzig, seidig, spitz, stachelig, stark, texturiert, trocken, Uneben, vibrierend, warm, w\u00e4ssrig, weich, wollig<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n"}},"NextChoiceId":199,"NextAnswerId":1,"SearchSource":{"AllowFreeResponse":"false"}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_82HJZMMWolInCCi","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID348","SecondaryAttribute":"\u00a0 Now, please describe how this touch makes you feel, emotionally \u00a0 Need some inspiration? I feel.","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n<div><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Now, please describe how this touch makes you feel, <em>emotionally<\/em><\/span><\/div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;<\/div>\n\n<div><span style=\"font-size:13px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Need some inspiration?<\/span><\/span><\/div>\n\n<div id=\"accordion4\">\n<div>\n<h3><span style=\"font-size:13px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">I feel<\/span><\/span><\/h3>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:107%\"><span style=\"font-family:&