n?<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Geben Sie entweder eine <em>kurze Beschreibung<\/em>, der Situation, die Sie sich gerade vorstellen, in das Textfeld ein.<br \/>\nM\u00f6chten Sie sich ein<button id=\"myBtn9\">Beispiel<\/button><\/span>ansehen?<\/p>\n\n<div class=\"modal\" id=\"myModal2\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\"><span class=\"close\">\u00d7<\/span>\n\n<h4><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Lassen Sie sich inspirieren<\/span><\/h4>\n<\/div>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">bei der Arbeit, in einer Arztpraxis, in einem Caf\u00e9, in einem Friseursalon, zu Hause, drau\u00dfen in der Natur, in einem Seminar, auf der Stra\u00dfe, Verkehrsmitteln, in \u00f6ffentlichen\u2026<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"modal\" id=\"myModal3\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\"><span class=\"close\">\u00d7<\/span>\n\n<h4><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Lassen Sie sich inspirieren<\/span><\/h4>\n<\/div>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">die gerade Ihren Beruf aus\u00fcbt (z.B. Friseur*in, Therapeut*in, Trainer*in), ein Familienmitglied, ein Kind, ein\/eine Bekannt*er, ein\/eine Freund*in, ein\/eine romantische Partner*ineine Person...<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"modal\" id=\"myModal4\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\"><span class=\"close\">\u00d7<\/span>\n\n<h4><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Lassen Sie sich inspirieren<\/span><\/h4>\n<\/div>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Ihr Bauch, Ihre Brust, Ihr Fu\u00df, Ihr Genitalbereich, Ihr Gesicht, Ihre Hand, Ihr Kopf, Ihr Nacken, Ihr Oberschenkel, Ihr Oberarm, Ihr R\u00fccken, Ihre Schulter, Ihr Unterarm, Ihr Unterschenkel...<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"modal\" id=\"myModal5\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\"><span class=\"close\">\u00d7<\/span>\n\n<h4><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Lassen Sie sich inspirieren<\/span><\/h4>\n<\/div>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">arbeiten, entspannen, gehen, kochen, kuscheln, putzen, streiten, sich vertragen...<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"modal\" id=\"myModal9\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\"><span class=\"close\">\u00d7<\/span>\n\n<h4><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Beispiel<\/span><\/h4>\n<\/div>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Mein Kollege st\u00f6\u00dft aus Versehen gegen meine Schulter, als wir den Flur entlang gehen.<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n"}},"NextChoiceId":80,"NextAnswerId":3,"SearchSource":{"AllowFreeResponse":"false"},"QuestionText_Unsafe":"What part of your body does the person touch? (it can be anywhere, besides the forearm)<br>","DataExportTag":"Q718","QuestionID":"QID718"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_82HJZMMWolInCCi","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID367","SecondaryAttribute":"What part of your body does the person touch? Need some inspiration? your back, your belly, your...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">What part of your body does the person touch?<\/span>\n<div id=\"accordion2\"><span style=\"font-size:13px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Need some inspiration?<\/span><\/span>\n<div><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:107%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">your back, your belly, your chest, your face, your foot, your forearm, your genital area, your hand, your head, your lower leg, your neck, your shoulder, your thigh, your upper arm ...<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/div>\n<\/div>","QuestionJS":"Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnload(function()\n{\n\t\/*Place your JavaScript here to run when the page loads*\/\n\n});\n\nQualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnReady(function()\n{\n\t\/*Place your JavaScript here to run when the page is fully displayed*\/\n\t\tjQuery( function() {\n        jQuery( \"#accordion2\" ).accordion({\n            active:false,\n             collapsible: true\n        });\n  } );\n\n});\n\nQualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnUnload(function()\n{\n\t\/*Place your JavaScript here to run when the page is unloaded*\/\n\n});","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Social_body_02","QuestionID":"QID367","QuestionType":"TE","Selector":"ESTB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"What part of your body does the person touch? Need some inspiration? your back, your belly, your...","Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"DE":{"QuestionText":"<h3><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Jetzt stellen Sie sich bitte eine soziale Interaktion vor, in der Sie auf diese Art ber\u00fchrt werden.<\/span><\/h3>\n\n<p><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Bedenken Sie dabei die folgenden Details<\/span><\/p>\n\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"column\">\n<ul>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Welcher<button id=\"myBtn4\">Bereich Ihres K\u00f6rpers<\/button> wird ber\u00fchrt?<\/span><\/li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\"><button id=\"myBtn2\">Wo<\/button>sind Sie?<\/span><\/li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\"><button id=\"myBtn3\">Wer<\/button>ist die Person, die Sie ber\u00fchrt?<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"column\">\n<ul>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\"><button id=\"myBtn5\">Was<\/button>tun Sie gerade?<\/span><\/li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Was ist die Absicht der Person, die Sie ber\u00fchrt?<\/span><\/li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Was passiert sonst noch in der entsprechenden Situation?<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Geben Sie entweder eine <em>kurze Beschreibung<\/em>, der Situation, die Sie sich gerade vorstellen, in das Textfeld ein.<br \/>\nM\u00f6chten Sie sich ein<button id=\"myBtn9\">Beispiel<\/button><\/span>ansehen?<\/p>\n\n<div class=\"modal\" id=\"myModal2\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\"><span class=\"close\">\u00d7<\/span>\n\n<h4><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Lassen Sie sich inspirieren<\/span><\/h4>\n<\/div>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">bei der Arbeit, in einer Arztpraxis, in einem Caf\u00e9, in einem Friseursalon, zu Hause, drau\u00dfen in der Natur, in einem Seminar, auf der Stra\u00dfe, Verkehrsmitteln, in \u00f6ffentlichen\u2026<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"modal\" id=\"myModal3\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\"><span class=\"close\">\u00d7<\/span>\n\n<h4><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Lassen Sie sich inspirieren<\/span><\/h4>\n<\/div>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">die gerade Ihren Beruf aus\u00fcbt (z.B. Friseur*in, Therapeut*in, Trainer*in), ein Familienmitglied, ein Kind, ein\/eine Bekannt*er, ein\/eine Freund*in, ein\/eine romantische Partner*ineine Person...<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"modal\" id=\"myModal4\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\"><span class=\"close\">\u00d7<\/span>\n\n<h4><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Lassen Sie sich inspirieren<\/span><\/h4>\n<\/div>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Ihr Bauch, Ihre Brust, Ihr Fu\u00df, Ihr Genitalbereich, Ihr Gesicht, Ihre Hand, Ihr Kopf, Ihr Nacken, Ihr Oberschenkel, Ihr Oberarm, Ihr R\u00fccken, Ihre Schulter, Ihr Unterarm, Ihr Unterschenkel...<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"modal\" id=\"myModal5\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\"><span class=\"close\">\u00d7<\/span>\n\n<h4><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Lassen Sie sich inspirieren<\/span><\/h4>\n<\/div>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">arbeiten, entspannen, gehen, kochen, kuscheln, putzen, streiten, sich vertragen...<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"modal\" id=\"myModal9\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\"><span class=\"close\">\u00d7<\/span>\n\n<h4><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Beispiel<\/span><\/h4>\n<\/div>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Mein Kollege st\u00f6\u00dft aus Versehen gegen meine Schulter, als wir den Flur entlang gehen.<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n"}},"NextChoiceId":80,"NextAnswerId":3,"SearchSource":{"AllowFreeResponse":"false"}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_82HJZMMWolInCCi","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID9","SecondaryAttribute":"What to expect... \u00a0 A short video clip. Please, watch the video carefully and feel free to play i..","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<h2><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;\"><strong>What to expect...<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/h2>\n\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n<p>A short video clip.<\/p>\n\n<p>Please, watch the video carefully and feel free to play it as many times as you want. It is best to watch the video in the highest possible quality, for which you can use the settings in the video player.<\/p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n<p>Questions regarding the video clip.<\/p>\n\n<p>Each question is followed by some exemplary answers<strong>. <br><\/strong><\/p><p><strong>If you don't find the most adequate choices, you may also type your own words to best describe<\/strong>. You can also select multiple answers for each question.<\/p>\n\n<div>&nbsp;<\/div>\n\n<div>What to do:<\/div>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\"><strong>Please focus on the video shown and answer the following questions, as detailed, and accurately as possible<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n\n<div>&nbsp;<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"modal\" id=\"myModal10\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\"><span class=\"close\">\u00d7<\/span><\/div>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Here you will find explanations, suggestions, and examples.<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>","QuestionJS":"Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnload(function()\n{\n\t\/*Place your JavaScript here to run when the page loads*\/\njQuery(\"div.ProgressBarFill\").css(\"width\", \"40%\");\n\t\n\nQualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnReady(function() \n{  \n  jQuery(\"table.ProgressBarContainer tbody tr td:eq(0) label\").text(\"40 %\"); \n}); \n});\n\nQualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnReady(function()\n{\n\t\/*Place your JavaScript here to run when the page is fully displayed*\/\n\t\t\/\/ Get the modal\n\tvar modal10 = document.getElementById(\"myModal10\");\n\n\t\/\/ Get the button that opens the modal\n\tvar btn10 = document.getElementById(\"myBtn10\");\n\t\n\t\/\/ Get the <span> element that closes the modal\n\tvar span10 = document.getElementsByClassName(\"close\")[0];\n\n\t\/\/ When the user clicks on the button, open the modal\n\tbtn10.onclick = function() {\n  \t\tmodal10.style.display = \"block\";\n\t}\n\n\t\/\/ When the user clicks on <span> (x), close the modal\n\tspan10.onclick = function() {\n  \t\tmodal10.style.display = \"none\";\n\t}\n\n\t\/\/ When the user clicks anywhere outside of the modal, close it\n\twindow.onclick = function(event) {\n  \t\tif (event.target == modal10) {\n    \tmodal10.style.display = \"none\";\n  \t}\n} \n\n});\n\nQualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnUnload(function()\n{\n\t\/*Place your JavaScript here to run when the page is unloaded*\/\n\n});","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Instruction","QuestionID":"QID9","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"What to expect... \u00a0 A short video clip. Please, watch the video carefully and feel free to play i...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"DE":{"QuestionText":"<h2><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;\"><strong>Was Sie erwartet...<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/h2>\n\n<p>\u00a0<\/p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Das folgende Video wurde w\u00e4hrend eines Experiments in unserem Labor aufgenommen.<br \/>\nDaher gibt es einige Details, die f\u00fcr die Beantwortung der Fragen nicht relevant sind:<\/span><\/p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">die Versuchsleiter tragen einen Laborkittel<\/span><\/li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">der Arm ist auf einem gr\u00fcnen Hintergrund positioniert\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">auf der Haut sind Markierungen zu sehen, die als Orientierungspunkte f\u00fcr den Ber\u00fchrenden dienten<\/span><\/li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">auf der Hand des Ber\u00fchrenden sind \u00a0bunte Punkte<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Bitte ignorieren Sie diese Details und konzentrieren Sie sich nur auf die Ber\u00fchrungsinteraktion.<\/span><br \/>\n\u00a0<\/h3>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Bitte sehen Sie sich die Videos in m\u00f6glichst hoher Qualit\u00e4t an. Sie k\u00f6nnen die Videoqualit\u00e4t \u00fcber die Einstellungen im Videoplayer anpassen. Das Video ist sehr kurz, Sie k\u00f6nnen es sich also ruhig mehrmals ansehen. \u00a0Wenn Sie auf die<u><button id=\"myBtn10\">gepunkteten W\u00f6rter<\/button><\/u>klicken, erhalten Sie Anregungen und Beispiele.<\/span><\/p>\n\u00a0\n\n<div>\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\"><strong>Bitte versuchen Sie, sich auf die gezeigten Ber\u00fchrungen zu konzentrieren und die folgenden Fragen so genau wie m\u00f6glich zu beantworten.<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n\n<div>\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"modal\" id=\"myModal10\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\"><span class=\"close\">\u00d7<\/span><\/div>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Hier werden Sie Erkl\u00e4rungen, Anregungen und Beispiele finden.<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n"}},"NextChoiceId":7,"NextAnswerId":1}},{"SurveyID":"SV_82HJZMMWolInCCi","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID400","SecondaryAttribute":"Where are you?","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Where are you?<br>","QuestionJS":"Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnload(function()\n{\n\t\/*Place your JavaScript here to run when the page loads*\/\n\tjQuery(\"#\"+this.questionId+\" .TextEntryBox\").css({\"width\":\"100%\", \"height\":\"4em\"});\n\t\t\n\t\/\/ Get the modal Where\n\tvar modal2 = document.getElementById(\"myModal2\");\n\n\t\/\/ Get the button that opens the modal\n\tvar btn2 = document.getElementById(\"myBtn2\");\n\t\t\n\t\/\/ Get the <span> element that closes the modal\n\tvar span2 = document.getElementsByClassName(\"close\")[1];\n\t\n\t\/\/ When the user clicks on the button, open the modal\n\tbtn2.onclick = function() {\n  \t\tmodal2.style.display = \"block\";\n\t}\n\n\t\/\/ When the user clicks on <span> (x), close the modal\n\tspan2.onclick = function() {\n  \t\tmodal2.style.display = \"none\";\n\t}\n\n\t\/\/ When the user clicks anywhere outside of the modal, close it\n\twindow.onclick = function(event) {\n  \t\tif (event.target == modal2) {\n    \tmodal2.style.display = \"none\";\n  \t}\n\t\n} \n\t\n\t\t\/\/ Get the modal Who\n\tvar modal3 = document.getElementById(\"myModal3\");\n\n\t\/\/ Get the button that opens the modal\n\tvar btn3 = document.getElementById(\"myBtn3\");\n\n\t\/\/ Get the <span> element that closes the modal\n\tvar span3 = document.getElementsByClassName(\"close\")[2];\n\n\t\/\/ When the user clicks on the button, open the modal\n\tbtn3.onclick = function() {\n  \t\tmodal3.style.display = \"block\";\n\t}\n\n\t\/\/ When the user clicks on <span> (x), close the modal\n\tspan3.onclick = function() {\n  \t\tmodal3.style.display = \"none\";\n\t}\n\n\t\/\/ When the user clicks anywhere outside of the modal, close it\n\twindow.onclick = function(event) {\n  \t\tif (event.target == modal3) {\n    \tmodal3.